Class PhotoController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.abqtrailsserverside.controller.PhotoController

  • @RestController
 @RequestMapping(value="photos")
 @ExposesResourceFor(value=Photo.class)
public class PhotoController
extends Object
    Defines REST endpoints for servicing requests on Photo resources, invoking PhotoRepository methods to perform the required operations.
